{"tid":1252864,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"個世界係咪就快玩完？","createTime":"2019-06-23T09:00:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-23T09:07:21.000Z","uid":86003,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f928800a8d2378ccf161ec68d743f9ead4e5d451","tid":1252864,"uid":86003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T09:00:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uUpq4PA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuUpq4PA.png&h=bfd1480c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我每晚臨訓前都會睇新聞<br />\n然後睇下個世界發生緊咩事<br />\n每一日自己又做緊啲咩事...<br />\n<br />\n世界另一邊每日都有人或者動物承受緊痛苦<br />\n而世界呢邊有人依然hehehaha 吃喝玩樂<br />\n盡情破壞浪廢地球<br />\n<br />\n究竟係咪我太認真？<br />\n有時真係覺得個世界好fuck up <br />\n但係我又可以做到啲咩<br />\n第二朝又繼續返一份對世界無咩貢獻嘅工<br />\n睇住班有錢人 政府 玩死個世界<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2383110/?r=mcsdfb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2383110%2F%3Fr%3Dmcsdfb&d=UYGl2U%2FUD6QdVJGaYMmpaPhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=41ad26db\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2383110/?r=mcsdfb</a>"},{"pid":"189888a4e40e9e980ca910f7b70ebf9ee0dea66b","tid":1252864,"uid":254923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T09:03:01.000Z","msg":"等死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64e111ed893f5f7df1ac9e82ae45825c132a75f9","tid":1252864,"uid":120070,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T09:04:11.000Z","msg":"正常 香港 會有既無力感超大<br />\n根本做唔到啲咩黎影響大環境"},{"pid":"c22d3ddf3f61d10925dca8dec412b78a2a028f48","tid":1252864,"uid":78666,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T09:06:14.000Z","msg":"正常氣候循環"},{"pid":"e8b2ed9fdde1d2d2946c8554bc85d8bd1edfdd24","tid":1252864,"uid":258566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T09:06:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fa8b21ebc2413174783739ca85ef522df45d884a","tid":1252864,"uid":48579,"like":0,"disli